{"tid":854523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(紅磚人請入) 轉咗新供應商 Poly新·舊Can貴到離曬譜","createTime":"2018-10-09T11:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T12:36:07.000Z","uid":45774,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb02a68c30fd54a27be8bfde7725bb03b7a2261c","tid":854523,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T11:59:10.000Z","msg":"佢老味 自從轉咗大家樂集團之後 貴到趴街<br />\n真係眼到凸埋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/195125_3335cdef2975141e877811c4ea967258.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F195125_3335cdef2975141e877811c4ea967258.png&h=4de1b5da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/195130_10e06fbe2fa2772de2aaf58d321602e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F195130_10e06fbe2fa2772de2aaf58d321602e2.png&h=837fd184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3字頭嘅選擇同2字頭嘅居然55波<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">熱飲加3蚊 凍飲加4.5</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n呢個真心屌咗出聲<br />\n<br />\n以前兩餸飯加凍飲都係23 24，飲凍綠茶仲唔洗加錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早餐又係<br />\n呢個雞扒多士炒蛋加細到爆嘅通粉，飲凍OT<br />\n居然要28蚊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/195400_526e7470ed38a3233b4b0cced6db6334.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F195400_526e7470ed38a3233b4b0cced6db6334.png&h=457cbc07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好懷念以前係成個公仔麵餅 都係23 24咋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02efee82cee0fcf62f143a1b970565ce08d3ff53","tid":854523,"uid":18411,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"教院仔表示好羨慕$24焗豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14db8596ce69f6da91814d3477dd54495bf42d55","tid":854523,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02efee82cee0fcf62f143a1b970565ce08d3ff53","tid":854523,"uid":18411,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"教院仔表示好羨慕$24焗豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:03:51.000Z","msg":"24蚊焗豬同21蚊焗肉醬意<br />\n真係勁良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我淨係食呢2個同兩餸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e101ec37300f1cd5c27b91ed63cda3d138f3b2","tid":854523,"uid":124140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"食過一次舊can 早餐後<br />\n覺得而家伏過以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49f888f606b37d6ce3d393129d0e8762cc6601a","tid":854523,"uid":45774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46e101ec37300f1cd5c27b91ed63cda3d138f3b2","tid":854523,"uid":124140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"食過一次舊can 早餐後<br />\n覺得而家伏過以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"以前真係好食好多<br />\n仲大份又抵食d"},{"pid":"ed590033a71f26dc4d401d7210dfc7f8aa568c19","tid":854523,"uid":167060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"重點係 好撚難食呀！"},{"pid":"36d7e1cb89576088234bded5c9f423a1b032245e","tid":854523,"uid":124140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e49f888f606b37d6ce3d393129d0e8762cc6601a","tid":854523,"uid":45774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46e101ec37300f1cd5c27